title: Make Iframe Youtube Videos Automatically Start Playing
tags: @zettel _method html
roam-id: 9420d941-8b16-48e8-bbba-8ed026207d6d
type: text/markdown

- add `?autoplay=1` at the end of the video id. see example below

``` html
<iframe
  src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9SbnhgjeyXA?autoplay=1">
</iframe>
```
